Summary:	Phorum is a web based message board written in PHP
Summary(pl.UTF-8):	Phorum - implementacja forum WWW w PHP
Name:		phorum
Version:	5.0.21
Release:	0.20
License:	Apache-like
Group:		Applications/WWW
Source0:	http://www.phorum.org/downloads/%{name}-%{version}.tar.bz2
